  "general_information": "The DHT Bronco is a very large crude carrier (VLCC) built by Hyundai Heavy Industries, with an IMO number of 9822994. It has a deadweight tonnage of 317,975dwt and a cargo capacity of 353,900m^3. The vessel features a Hyundai Hi-Bow design and a Hi-PSD propeller swirl duct for improved fuel efficiency. It is equipped with an Alfa Laval PureSOx system for exhaust gas scrubbing and has a maximum loading capacity of 20,500m^3/h.",
